The pump price of premium motor spirit (PMS) popularly known as petrol has been increased to N151.56 per litre. The increase is expected to take effect from September 2, 2020. This was disclosed on Wednesday in a memo by the Pipeline and Product Marketing Company (PPMC), Ibadan depot, to all the stakeholders and signed by the Depot Manager, D.O. Abalaka. Details shortlyâ€¦